Universal Logic, Inc., formerly Universal Robotics, Inc., is an artificial intelligence software engineering and robotics integration company headquartered in Nashville, Tennessee.The Company was founded in 2008 by brothers, David and Alan Peters.  In 2015, the company received its first million-dollar contract.

Leadership
Universal Robotics is led by David Peters, CEO, Nick Buchta, President, and Goutham Mallapragada, CTO. 


